Key Match Events: The game start time was moved up due to weather
The Tigers were eliminated from the playoffs after a 7-3 loss in Game 5
Post-Match Reflections: The Tigers' elimination marked the end of their playoff journey
Fans set another postseason attendance record at Comerica Park
Miscellaneous Highlights: Weather delays led to the game being postponed until the next day
